{"tid":788863,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"美國NASA最新確認：月球極地有H2O","createTime":"2018-08-21T21:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T07:10:14.000Z","uid":165773,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"232d1451f1014405d4d13c95192198fcf0f74d9f","tid":788863,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T21:58:00.000Z","msg":"今個星期一<br />\n美國NASA引用<br />\n印度登月探測器M3<br />\n所收集數據確認<br />\n<br />\n月球極地附近發現大量冰塊 <br />\n溫度低過 -250 &deg;F<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/22/055205_ebcc2dbfc6365ea4a5432a6e5fbe6e7d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F22%2F055205_ebcc2dbfc6365ea4a5432a6e5fbe6e7d.png&h=618e3c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信日後登月可以用作補充水源<br />\n甚至補充燃料（H2 +O2）<br />\n<br />\nIt's NASA Official: The Moon Has Water Ice Deposits in Its Frozen Craters<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inverse.com/article/48281-nasa-moon-water-ice-deposits-in-craters\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inverse.com%2Farticle%2F48281-nasa-moon-water-ice-deposits-in-craters&d=bkn8ywxYB2KZgfajZiddNBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=351fb49d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inverse.com/article/48281-nasa-moon-water-ice-deposits-in-craters</a>"},{"pid":"89ddf7fd71c1c4312f99cf95e66771f57dfd0d3d","tid":788863,"uid":108358,"like":16,"dislike":6,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T22:03:14.000Z","msg":"差23度西伯利亞人就可以移居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ceaa700962bebf987395a84e14fff5d3ce925c1","tid":788863,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T22:04:19.000Z","msg":"唔係有基地咩"},{"pid":"408cef5fc4b914e9d1cce3d62f962cc31e9b268c","tid":788863,"uid":86199,"like":25,"dislike":4,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"89ddf7fd71c1c4312f99cf95e66771f57dfd0d3d","tid":788863,"uid":108358,"like":16,"dislike":6,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T22:03:14.00